This add-on allows you to obtain graphical forms to change add-on configurations.

<img src="https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-gui-for-addon-config/raw/master/copy.png"/>
<img src="https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-gui-for-addon-config/raw/master/ff.png"/>

It only works with add-on which were made compatible with the current add-on; which is really easy to do. To report bug, and for more informations, please go to https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-gui-for-addon-config

<strong>SUPPORT THIS ADD-ON</strong>

